data.title: The Republic of Malta
data.meta_description: Malta, officially The Republic of Malta, is a country in Europe, with an area of 316 square kilometers and a population of around 514,564. Its gdp is $14,786.16 Millions(2019). The capital of Malta Valletta, and the official currency is Euro(EUR).
data.text:
Malta, officially The Republic of Malta, is a country in Europe, with an area of 316 square kilometers and a population of around 514,564. Its gdp is $14,786.16 Millions(2019). The capital of Malta Valletta, and the official currency is Euro(EUR).
